14. Be2
14. Qd6{ Clearing the way for the rook. }
15. Na4
15. Rae8
16. Rc1
16. Ne4{ The knight is dominant and outweighs the fact that Black is losing his bishop pair. }( 17.Nxb6 axb6 18.Nh4 { , 0-1 (40),  Hossain  (2452) -  Ibarra Jerez  (2564), Batumi 2018. }{ I'd like to recommend the next regrouping: }18...Bxe2 19.Qxe2 Qd7 { Making a place for the knight to  d6 . }20.Nf3 Nd6⩱ { Followed by with ... Nf5  and doubling across the e-file. } )
