11. Rxd5{ In for a penny, in for a pound! }
12. exd5
12. Re8{ It transpires that we are still in mainstream theory, with too many strong contenders playing this position for both sides. Black intends to force a breakthrough across the e-file, using the rook as a battering ram. }
13. c3
