9. Bg4{ White is just too underdeveloped. We will soon put a rook at  e8  when White will be calling '911'. }
10. Nf3
10. O-O
11. cxb4
11. Nxf3+{ Time to harvest! }
12. gxf3
12. Re8{ Black's attack is continuing at a rapid pace. }
