11. Qd7{ This is a novelty. The main line is  11..O-O  and has been played multiple times. However, I'd rather go for the surprising effect while maintaining a pleasant edge. }( { The main line goes }11...O-O 12.Nc3 Re8 13.a4 b4 14.Ne4 Bb7 15.Nf5 Qd7 { when Black was slightly better in ½-½ (24),  Jaederholm  (2490) -  Hiltunen  (2496), ICCF email 2007. } )
