5. O-O
5. Be7
6. d4{ The so-called Center Attack, the one in which White doesn't beat around the bush but strikes without hesitation in the center. What is in the name! }
6. exd4{ Even though we allow  e4 - e5 , we are not afraid since we have the solid knight redeployment on  c5  at sight. }
