11. Nh4
11. Nf8{ On its way to green pastures. }
12. Nf5
12. Bc5{ The idea is to chase the knight with ... g6 , not giving up on the bishop pair. }
13. a4
13. Ne6{ The knight reached its destination. From  e6 , it's impeding  f2 - f4  and could be moved to  d4  at any given moment. }
14. Kh1
14. b5{ Gaining space and stopping  Nc4 . Black was comfortable in  Gomila Marti  (2334) -  Fernandez  (2414), ½-½ (29), ICCF email 2017. }
