16. dxe5
17. Nxe5
17. Bb7{ The bishop is a stronger piece than the knight, moreover, there are many weaknesses, i.e.,  d5  and  e3 . }
18. e4
18. Qe7
19. Qd4{ Black, regaining the pawn, is OK here. }
