19. g5( { White should refrain from taking, as the Chinese GM  Bu  showed: }20.fxg5? Rf3! 21.Rad1 Qe6-+ { , 0-1 (28),  Z. Tan  (2525) -  Bu  (2705), Liaocheng 2021. } )
