14. gxf3
14. Bb6{ Black's position was to be preferred in  Zholob  (2095) -  Joensson  (1992), ½-½ (28), LSS email 2019. }{ The queen enters the fray by ... Qc8 - h3  while after castling, we could proceed with ... f7 - f5 . }
