9. Be6{ Plain and square. The best white piece is about to be exchanged. }( 9...Bg4?! { only helps the white queen to a better square: }10.Qd3 Be6 11.Bg5 Bxc4 12.Qxc4=∞ { , 0-1 (82),  Paravyan  (2653) -  Firouzja  (2728), lichess.org 2020. } )
10. Bd3
10. Qd6{ Black is much better since he will improve his king's position after long castling. }
