6. Bd3( { This is one of them! According to Gustafsson, in his  1.e4 e5  Lifetime Repertoires, this is a logical and very solid move, and I agree, as it is a decent developing move whereas it doesn't allow any pins after }6.Nc3 Bb4 { . } )
