8. O-O
8. O-O
9. Nbd2( { The plan to capture the  f4 -pawn with  Nb1 - c3 - e2 - xf4  falls short, as after }9.Nc3 { , Black seizes the initiative with }9...h6! 10.Ne2 { and }10...g5∓ { . } )
