15. b3{ Now white will try to capitalize on our oddly placed knights, with  b3  they attempt to exclude the knights from the game. }
15. c4{ Black is now trying to create a square for the knight on  c5 . }
16. b4{ White is doing the same, stopping the knight from getting to  c5 . }
16. a5{ Of course, a logical move, trying to get some play on the a-file. }
