26. Nxe5{ White wants to get rid of the strong knight of course, but this comes at a concession. }
26. fxe5{ We traded our worst placed piece, the knight on  b7  to an improved pawn structure (now there's no more minority attack possible on the kingside) and also the dark-squared bishop improved, the knight on  g3  is completely out of the game and in the meantime black is just much better strategically. }
