22. c4( 22...gxf5 { looks like white is just giving up a piece for not so much compensation, but it is just too risky to open up the g-file. }23.gxf5 Ng7 24.Qg4 { followed by the tripling of the heavy pieces definitely gives some white some chances.    There's no need at all to open up the g-file. } )
