{ Welcome everyone, in this model game we are going to have a look at the game Vladimir Kramnik with the black pieces playing the Scottish main line against Nadev. The game was played in the Olympiad in Tromso 2014 and Vladimir Kramnik kind of tackled most of the problems for black in this game. Very nice game and I want to come also with an improvement here. }1. e4
